Application of oil-in-water nanoemulsions based on grape and cinnamon essential 
oils for shelf-life extension of chilled flathead mullet fillets.

Ameur A(1), Bensid A(2), Ozogul F(3), Ucar Y(3), Durmus M(3), Kulawik P(4), 
